      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLINK AND MISS (4) sizzled around 500m in 27.94 when winning a Group Listed at Bendigo last start. In form and looks the one to beat again. FLAMING SMOOTH (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.2 lengths at Sandown in a handy 29.50 beating Moonlight Miller. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Likely to be in the finish. WIZARD WATSON (7) is in hot form after clocking a sharp 25.86 victory two back then followed up with a 24.99 win at Shepparton over 450m last time. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. MEPUNGA SAGE (8) hit the frame latest (30.47) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw.",
